metadata:
  id: guidelines-index
  version: 1.0
  lastUpdated: 2025-11-19
  description: "Index of all guidelines. Load specific guidelines on-demand using @path syntax."

usage: |
  This index allows progressive context loading. Instead of loading all guidelines,
  Claude should:
  1. Consult this index to find relevant guidelines by ID or topic
  2. Load only the specific guideline needed using @.claude/guidelines/[path]
  3. Reference guideline IDs for cross-linking

  Example: For naming questions, load @.claude/guidelines/03-code-standards/3.1-naming-conventions.toon

